OL,5,G1400 A Place in the Sun
OL,6,     FDanni Menzies helps Anne and Ian
OL,7,     Ffrom the Scottish Highlands find
OL,8,     Ftheir perfect holiday home in the
OL,9,     Fbuzzing resort of Benidorm on
OL,10,     FSpain's Costa Blanca, for their
OL,11,     Fbudget of #100,000.
OL,12,G1500 A Place in the Sun
OL,13,     FDabi and Devi can't wait to swap
OL,14,     Fthe grey skies of Croydon for the
OL,15,     Fsunshine and heat in the seaside
OL,16,     Ftown of Gandia in Valencia. Lee
OL,17,     FJuggurnauth shows them what their
OL,18,     F#180k budget can buy.
